CONCRETE IMPLEMENTATION PATTERNS AND BEST PRACTICES

- To add a new feature:
  1) Create new source under src/lib/ with ES module exports.
  2) Add unit tests under tests/unit/ corresponding to behaviour.
  3) Run npm run test:unit locally, address failures, then open PR.
  4) Ensure agentic-lib.toml paths include any new directories if agents must scan them.

- To adjust agent schedule: set [schedule].supervisor in agentic-lib.toml to one of allowed values; commit and push to trigger changed agent cadence.

